"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president gave a long speech where he spoke to his supporters and mocked his opponents. He claimed that the US is winning again and talked about his achievements.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Speech\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Estados Unidos dio un discurso largo donde habl\u00f3 a sus seguidores y se burl\u00f3 de sus oponentes. Dijo que Estados Unidos est\u00e1 ganando otra vez y habl\u00f3 de sus logros.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Discurso del Presidente de EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Guadalajara, people are reacting after cartel members tried to take revenge for the killing of Nemesio 'El Mencho' Oseguera.\",            \"english_title\": \"Reactions in Guadalajara\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Guadalajara, la gente est\u00e1 reaccionando despu\u00e9s de que miembros del cartel intentaron vengarse por la muerte de Nemesio 'El Mencho' Oseguera.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Reacciones en Guadalajara\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Zimbabwe is concerned because the US does not want to share the benefits of research from biological samples.\",            \"english_title\": \"Zimbabwe's Concern\",            \"translated_version\": \"Zimbabue est\u00e1 preocupado porque Estados Unidos no quiere compartir los beneficios de la investigaci\u00f3n de muestras biol\u00f3gicas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaci\u00f3n de Zimbabue\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"On the remote Yonaguni island, there are rising tensions between self-governing Taiwan and China.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tensions on Yonaguni Island\",            \"translated_version\": \"En la isla remota de Yonaguni, hay tensiones crecientes entre Taiw\u00e1n, que se gobierna solo, y China.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tensiones en la Isla Yonaguni\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Events took place across Ukraine to remember four years since Russia started its full-scale invasion.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine Remembers\",            \"translated_version\": \"Se realizaron eventos en toda Ucrania para recordar cuatro a\u00f1os desde que Rusia comenz\u00f3 su invasi\u00f3n a gran escala.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ucrania Recuerda\"        }    ]}"